git clone https://github.com/CMU-Perceptual-Computing-Lab/openpose

cd openpose

git submodule update --init --recursive --remote

Use CMake app, origin openpose folder, output openpose/build

make -j`sysctl -n hw.logicalcpu`

 Go to build/caffe/src/openpose_lib-build/CMakeCache.txt and manually change this:
vecLib_INCLUDE_DIR:PATH=vecLib_INCLUDE_DIR-NOTFOUND to

vecLib_INCLUDE_DIR:PATH=/Library/Developer/CommandLineTools/SDKs/MacOSX.sdk/System/Library/Frameworks/Accelerate.framework/Versions/Current/Frameworks/vecLib.framework/Headers/

Go to 3rdparty/caffe/CMakeList.txt change version c++ to 17

Go to openpose/3rdparty/caffe/src/caffe/layers/hdf5_data_layer.cpp

Change std::random_shuffle with:

#include <algorithm>  // For std::shuffle
#include <random>     // For random number generators

std::random_device rd;            // Obtain a random number from hardware
std::mt19937 generator(rd());     // Seed the generator
std::shuffle(file_permutation_.begin(), file_permutation_.end(),generator);

Go to: openpose/3rdparty/caffe/src/caffe/util/io.cpp

Go to CMakeLists.txt in openpose and change c++ version everywhere and also change the line if 
if (APPLE)
  include_directories("/usr/local/opt/openblas/include")
endif (APPLE)
to
(APPLE)
  include_directories("/opt/homebrew/opt/openblas/include")
endif (APPLE)


